        <pre data-prefix=">" class="text-success"><code>Use standard DaisyUI classes</code></pre>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-black mt-12 mb-6">What's Included</h2>
      
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-lg mb-12">
        <li>Complete color system (light + dark modes)</li>
        <li>Typography scale with custom font weights</li>
